40|$|Una verifica empirica del ciclo elettorale <b>nelle</b> <b>scelte</b> di politica fiscale dei governi locali marchigiani - In {{this paper}} we conduct a dynamic panel data {{analysis}} using 246 municipalities of the Marche region {{in order to}} investigate the presence of electoral budget cycle in local tax setting. Results show that local governments significantly decrease property tax rate during the election year. Although incumbent politicians can choose the tax rate in a range from 4 % to 7 %, results highlight that the range is not a hindrance to engaging electoral competition at the local government level. ...|$|R
